        "TileImage": "$($repository 8943b399-8e00-4a7b-ae79-41863722c45a).Image",
        "Description": "Today, the Dartmoor estate is being divided up for the inheritance of the last family&apos;s murder. However, there is one black sheep of the family named Alexa Carlisle. She is an old lady who has started a shady business. She has started manipulating the rest of the family to get as much of the inheritance money as possible. She has also hired a fake lawyer named Aron Ford Jr, who is trying to feed the family lies and false information. Good luck.",
